18
00:02:22.038 --> 00:02:36.818
Sometimes you need a sequence. Imagine a mixture of sand,
salt, and iron filings. First use a magnet for the iron.
Then add water to dissolve the salt. Filter out the sand.

19
00:02:36.818 --> 00:02:47.638
That sounds like several steps because the mixture has
several different properties to exploit. Size, solubility,
and magnetism each give you a different handle.

20
00:02:47.638 --> 00:03:01.313
