23
00:03:24.220 --> 00:03:33.887
So separation is a planning problem. Identify the parts,
list their properties, then pick the method that uses the
biggest useful difference between them.

24
00:03:33.887 --> 00:03:38.609
The separation question is: what property lets me separate
these parts?
